                  <p><span style="color:#000000">House of Lords </span><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Lords/2024-09-04/debates/79CA58AD-63C4-4A70-8F91-420445132015/ProductRegulationAndMetrologyBill(HL)"><span style="color:#0070C0"><u>Vol. 839 Col. 1158</u></span></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">Second Reading</span></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><span style="color:#000000">08 October 2024</span></p>
                </td>
